&lt;p&gt;The ideal candidate is well versed in aerospace production environment and has direct experience with supporting the production floor, DFM, machining, assembly, coating, metrology, &amp;amp; thrives on solving complex shop floor problems, and brings a strong process mindset to drive quality, speed, and consistency.&lt;/p&gt;
