&lt;li&gt;Partner with Finance and functional leaders to ensure operational plans support strategic and financial objectives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead continuous improvement initiatives by evaluating existing processes, identifying inefficiencies and opportunities, partnering with functional leaders to design improved ways of working, and driving measurable improvements to operational performance.&lt;/li&gt;
