&lt;p data-start=&quot;1381&quot; data-end=&quot;1553&quot;&gt;This role requires someone who thrives in a fast-paced, high-expectation environment and knows how to balance high-volume tactical execution with strategic hiring advisory.&lt;/p&gt;
